 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Ticket fraud inquiry involving LTS rail on day of privatisation </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Ticket fraud inquiry involving LTS rail on day of privatisation </b><br><br><br><b><h2>7 February 1996</h2></b><br><h2>British Rail suspends four staff in ticket fraud inquiry  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Keith Harper</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Four members of the ticketing staff on the London, Tilbury and Southend (LTS) line were yesterday suspended by British Rail pending further inquiries into allegations of fraud on the issuing of tickets which has cost London Transport up to &#163;45,000 in lost revenue.  <p>  <p>The suspensions were carried out as a precautionary measure while BR continues its inquiries. Three staff are at Southend, and a fourth is based at Fenchurch Street, London, where the ticket fraud emanated. BR has already carried out a systematic examination of possible frauds at other London stations and has discovered a minor problem at Walthamstow station, where 30 tickets have aroused suspicions.  <p>  <p>BR's inquiry is being conducted alongside an inquiry by the Rail Regulator, John Swift. The Government last night was still hoping it will be completed in time for Enterprise Rail, the private operator of the LTS line, to start operations next month.  <p>  <p>Enterprise Rail's financial backers, including the venture capital groups 3i and the Gresham Trust, are awaiting the inquiry's outcome before deciding if they should withdraw support.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
