 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Oil tanker Sea Empress founders on rocks off Milford  Haven</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Oil tanker Sea Empress founders on rocks off Milford Haven</b><br><br><br><b><h2>20 February  1996</h2></b><br><h2>Rare starfish caught in fallout over spill from tanker  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Owen Bowcott</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>A colony of 3,000 rare green rockpool starfish has been wiped out by crude oil leaking from the  holed tanker Sea Empress, according to wildlife groups in West Wales.  <p>  <p>Conservationists and government agencies were yesterday disputing the extent of environmental  damage to the shoreline of the Pembrokeshire National Park caused by oil from the stricken tanker,  which ran aground on Thursday on rocks at the entrance of the Milford Haven estuary.  <p>  <p>The Dyfed Wild Life Trust mourned the destruction of habitats in West Angle Bay at the mouth of the  estuary. The inlet had been "one of the best teaching sites in the whole of the British Isles for  future marine biologists", said Robin Crump, a trust official.  <p>  <p>The green rockpool starfish, the size of a 50p piece, may never re-colonise the bay. Unlike other  starfish, this variety - Latin name Asterina phylactica - does not have a free-swimming stage but  broods its eggs clinging to the rocks. The bay is one of only seven sites where the starfish has been  recorded in British waters.  <p>  <p>The World Wide Fund for Nature has voiced fear that other rare marine invertebrates, such as soft  corals, jewel anemones, sea fans and sea gooseberries, could suffer from oil coating the sea bed.  Wildlife groups said they believed porpoises and dolphins could also be at risk. But Malcolm Smith of  the Countryside Council for Wales, said environmental damage might not be as extensive as initially  suspected. A survey of Milford Haven found 13,000 sea birds, of which only 43 were oiled. "I do not think that we can be sure yet that the whole population of the green rockpool starfish  has been entirely killed off. We just don't know," he said.  <p>  <p>As for the seals, marine mammals do not have feathers to preen and were far less likely to ingest  oil than birds. Although the damage to the sea bird sanctuaries on Skomer and Skokholm could be  extremely serious, the oil slicks were of a light crude grade, being broken up rapidly by high winds  that have hindered the salvage operation.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center