 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Oil tanker Sea Empress founders on rocks off Milford  Haven</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Oil tanker Sea Empress founders on rocks off Milford Haven</b><br><br><br><b><h2>28 February  1996</h2></b><br><h2>Oil from tanker keeps fishing boats in port</h2><h3>Fishermen and merchants set up group  to fight for compensation  </h3>  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Paul Brown</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Fishing in the extensive shellfish grounds off Milford Haven, Dyfed, has been temporarily abandoned  because of oil contamination from the tanker Sea Empress. Nearly 300 fishermen and fish merchants meeting in Milford Haven voted to keep their boats in  harbour and set up an action group to draw up demands for compensation. The industry was worth &#163;7m a year before the spill, but foreign customers have cancelled  orders for crabs, lobsters and wet fish in the aftermath of widespread pollution off Pembrokeshire.  <p>  <p>The Government is expected to announce details soon of an official fishing exclusion zone in the  polluted area after studying reports from scientists. Trawler skipper David Bray, local secretary of  the Welsh Coastal Inshore Fishermen's Association, said: "We must try to keep public confidence in our  industry and in the quality of catches. In the meantime our members have no income and little prospect  of any. It is vital that compensation payments are arranged as quickly as possible."  <p>  <p>Madeline Moore runs a small family firm, Oneida, which buys winkles, lobsters, spider crabs and  prawns from fishermen and ships them live to the Continent. She said: "I don't think people understand  how serious this is. People keep saying they hope it will be alright, but it's not going to be." She  has contacted fishing groups affected by the Braer oil spill in Shetland in 1993 and has not been  heartened by their message. It took three months for fish to be allowed back on the market, 18 months  for most kinds of shellfish to be deemed clean, and prawns are still affected. Conservationists  demanded a full public inquiry. The Government's proposed inquiry by departmental marine accident  investigators was dismissed as inadequate.  <p>  <p>Much of the Pembrokeshire Coast National Park is heavily polluted by oil, with some wildlife rescue  services predicting that the eventual death toll of seabirds could reach 50,000 - the worst  environmental disaster since the Torrey Canyon wreck in 1967.  <p>  <p>The Council for National Parks said the initial refusal to allow the damaged Sea Empress into  Milford Haven may have been a crucial factor in subsequent pollution.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
