 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - CS gas used to subdue Rugby League international</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>CS gas used to subdue Rugby League international</b><br><br><br><b><h2>4 March 1996</h2></b><br><h2>CS gas subdues rugby forward  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Gary Younge</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Police used CS gas spray for the first time yesterday against a rugby league international who allegedly resisted arrest in Oldham, Greater Manchester.  <p>  <p>Police say that four officers were unable to restrain Barrie McDermott, aged 23, after the Great Britain forward became aggressive outside a nightclub in the early yesterday morning.  <p>  <p>A taxi driver called the police after Mr McDermott, who plays for Leeds, allegedly kicked his car door.  <p>  <p>A police spokesman said: "The CS spray was deployed, which was effective in subduing the man sufficiently for him to be restrained and placed under arrest.  <p>  <p>"Without the spray, it appears that an officer would have been injured." Speaking from his home near the club's ground in Headingley, Leeds, West Yorkshire, Mr McDermott said: "I have been advised by police not to say anything."  <p>  <p>Mr McDermott was suspended for five matches by the Rugby League disciplinary committee while playing for Wigan last year, after he was sent off for headbutting in a reserve game. In December he was dismissed in a game against Warrington for a "mistimed shoulder charge".  <p>  <p>After yesterday's arrest Mr McDermott, who has a glass eye after a childhood accident, was given medical treatment in accordance with procedure and "appears to have suffered no lasting effects from the spray", the spokesman said.  <p>  <p>He spent the night in custody, but has not been charged and was released on bail pending further enquiries.  <p>  <p>The spray was issued to more than 2,000 policemen in 16 forces in England and Wales on Friday for a six-month trial.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
