 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Trevor Nunn appointed as director of National Theatre</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Trevor Nunn appointed as director of National Theatre</b><br><br><br><b><h2>6 March 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Trevor Nunn to be National Theatre director  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Michael Ellison</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Trevor Nunn, the millionaire director of the musicals 'Cats' and 'Les Miserables', will be named today as the new director of the National Theatre. Mr Nunn, the former artistic director of the Royal Shakespeare Company (RSC), will become the fourth man to take charge of the National, on the south bank of the Thames, in its 34 years. He will follow Laurence Olivier, Peter Hall and Richard Eyre.  <p>  <p>Stephen Daldry of the Royal Court, Sam Mendes of the Donmar Warehouse, and Jude Kelly of the West Yorkshire Playhouse had been considered among the frontrunners for a job no one was prepared to say they wanted. All are much younger than Mr Nunn, aged 56, who will take over from Mr Eyre in 18 months. Indeed, Mr Nunn is four years older than Mr Eyre. "You don't give the National to some young thruster who wants to enhance his career," one observer said last night.  <p>  <p>"But Eyre is a class act and a very hard one to follow, in critical terms and at the box office. The big challenge for Nunn is to show he can still command a big classical stage, something he hasn't done since the early 1980s."  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
