http://www.guardian.co.uk:80/g96/articles/g96-482.html 194.205.4.11 19970222174943 text/html 5013
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 17:47:58 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.3
