 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - World Chess championship to be held in Baghdad</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>World Chess championship to be held in Baghdad</b><br><br><br><b><h2>9 March 1996</h2></b><br><h2>US bars American from world title challenge in Iraq  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Leonard Barden</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Saddam Hussein may be checkmated on 1 June after the United States state department stepped in to ban the American Gata Kamsky from playing his international federation (Fide) world title match in Baghdad. <p><p>On Thursday evening the Fide president Kirsan Ilyumzhinov made the astonishing announcement that the 20-game championship series between Kamsky and the holder, Russia's Anatoly Karpov, would be played in Iraq after Montreal had failed to guarantee its bid.  Saddam offered a &#163;1.3m prize fund, of which a quarter was to be donated to Unicef to buy medicines for Iraqi children.  But a few minutes after Ilyumzhinov, a caviar and oil millionaire who is head of the small Russian republic of Kalmykia, claimed at a Paris press conference that chess was not affected by UN sanctions, he had to retract after receiving news of the US action.  <p>  <p>If Baghdad is ruled out, Moscow and Baku will be favourites to stage the Karpov versus Kamsky match, which should have been played last year but was refused in turn by Hyderabad, Paris and St Petersburg.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC