 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - EU fishing commissioner Emma Bonino visits Cornish fishing areas </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>EU fishing commissioner Emma Bonino visits Cornish fishing areas </b><br><br><br><b><h2>20 March 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Permissive EU states allow boats to flout fishing policy  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Stephen Bates</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>European efforts to crack down on illegal fishing by national fleets under the EU's common fisheries policy have been woefully inadequate, according to the results of an official survey yesterday.  <p>  <p>The report, on how thoroughly the EU's member states police the policy, last night looked likely to revive British fishermen's complaints about the unfairness of the policy in the wake of the weekend visit to Britain of Emma Bonino, the Italian fisheries commissioner.  But the 105-page survey, based on monitoring in 1994, shows that British inspections are also inadequate due to the shortage of qualified inspectors to monitor catches at the dockside and that the chief culprits over illegal fishing have been British boats.  <p>  <p>The European Commission report says: "There are very big differences in the level of inspection between the various member states. The current lack of co-operation may reflect the permissive attitude towards the national fishing industries which attempt to exploit fishing possibilities beyond the limits set in accordance with the common fisheries policy. As long as the fishing industry in most member states exploits such fishing possibilities, none of them will gain, but obviously the conservation of fish stocks will be undermined for everyone."  <p>  <p>Of Britain, the report praises the inspection service's efficiency and competence and the significant resources devoted to control fishing, but says that limits to catches are extremely difficult to monitor. The report shows that, of 371 infringements notified, including illegal fishing and undersized fish catches, British vessels were responsible for 119, the French for 73, the Irish 62 and the Spanish - usual victims of British criticism - for just 22.  <p>  <p>The commission says: "Apart from some shortcomings... concerning the closure of fisheries and the prosecution of infringements, the means and the commitment invested in control and inspection in the UK provide an example of how the CFP should be enforced."  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
