 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Unabomber suspect, Theodore Kaczynskis held</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Unabomber suspect, Theodore Kaczynsk, held</b><br><br><br><b><h2>4 April 1996</h2></b><br><h2>'Unabomber' suspect held  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Ian Katz</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>The FBI appeared to have made a huge breakthrough in its 18-year hunt for a technophobic serial bomber yesterday when federal agents detained a former university professor they believe may be the so-called Unabomber. Theodore Kaczynski, understood to be a Harvard graduate and an academic at the University of California, at Berkeley, was reportedly taken into custody when he tried to prevent agents from searching his home in a remote area near Lincoln, Montana.  <p>  <p>It is believed that the FBI had been monitoring him for several weeks. Agents reportedly zeroed in on him after a lawyer approached the FBI in Washington on behalf of a man who feared the Unabomber might be his brother. The ingenious terrorist has mocked his pursuers for almost two decades, killing three people and injuring 23 in his sporadic bombing campaign against academics and executives associated with technology. In the most bizarre twist of the Unabomber saga, two of America's most respected newspapers, the New York Times and the Washington Post, in September published a 35,000 word 'manifesto' written by the bomber. Since then a huge FBI task force has enlisted the help of more than 60 academics in the hope of identifying the bomber's intellectual fingerprints. The agency also offered a $1m reward.  <p>  <p>According to reports yesterday, agents sought permission to search the Chicago home of the suspect's family after receiving a tip-off. They are said to have found documents and other material linking the man to the explosions.  <p>  <p>The bomber was dubbed Unabomber in the late Seventies because of his choice of targets. His devices have become increasingly sophisticated since a crude pipe bomb injured a security guard at Northwestern University, Illinois, in 1978.  <p>  <p>The hunt for him has been frustrated by the fact that he has been spotted only once, while planting a bomb in a Salt Lake City car park. He did not strike after that for several years.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
