 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Cunard liner Royal Viking Sun hits a coral reef in Red  Sea</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Cunard liner Royal Viking Sun hits a coral reef in Red Sea</b><br><br><br><b><h2>5 April  1996</h2></b><br><h2>World's top liner adrift with 1,000 aboard after collision  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Barbie Dutter</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>A luxury cruise liner with around 1,000 people on board was adrift without engine power in the Red  Sea early today after being holed when it hit an unidentified object. The Royal Viking Sun, owned by Cunard Line, began listing and taking in water after the collision  as it entered the Gulf of Aqaba, between Egypt and Jordan.  <p>  <p>The eight-year-old ship, which boasts five-star facilities and is the world's top-rated liner, was  part-way through a 114-day world cruise for which passengers had paid at least &#163;20,000 each.  <p>  <p>Bill Spears, Cunard's public relations director, said from New York that there was no panic on  board and the situation was "under control". "The ship is in no immediate danger and nor are the  passengers and crew," said Mr Spears.  <p>  <p>"The ship is drifting but the seas are calm. She hit a submerged object and has lost main  propulsion because of the water which entered the generating room and the engine room. But we have now  pumped quite a lot of it out and we have emergency power which is keeping services such as the pumps  operating."  <p>  <p>The 37,845-tonne, 669ft-long Royal Viking Sun had been heading towards the Jordanian port of Aqaba  on a trip from the Yemen. There were 500 passengers on board, mostly British, American and Australian,  and an international crew of a similar number.  <p>  <p>Two tugs were sent from Aqaba and were due to reach the ship by midday today to tow the liner to  the most accessible port and allow the passengers to disembark.  <p>  <p>Mr Spears said there was no indication of the nature of the object which holed the ship.  <p>  <p>A rescue service spokesman said: "The situation is stable, the list has been corrected and the  water is being pumped out. She has lost her main engines and is drifting but there are other vessels close by that will  assist."  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
