 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Drug tests introduced at Eton</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Drug tests introduced at Eton</b><br><br><br><b><h2>6 April 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Eton headmaster  brings in drug tests  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Alex Bellos</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Eton public school has introduced drug testing. Headmaster John Lewis's decision, announced in the  end-of-term newsletter, comes a year after a series of drugs scandals at the school.  <p>  <p>Eton is the most famous of a growing number of private schools, including Marlborough, Sevenoaks  and Ardingly, that tests pupils suspected of taking drugs as a means of deterrence.  <p>  <p>Mr Lewis told parents: "The headmaster may require any boy to submit to a urine or other  appropriate test whether on suspicion of the use of illicit drugs or other harmful substances, or at  his sole discretion, and may cause a search to be carried out of any boy's personal possessions or  room." He also reminded pupils that discipline can be breached at holidays and weekends. Even though  drug-taking was not mentioned explicitly, it is widely understood to mean that pupils may be tested  for what they may have experimented with outside the school gates.  <p>  <p>John Sutton, general secretary of the Secondary Heads Association, said many boarding schools felt  obliged to introduce anti-drugs measures to protect their reputations. Tales of drugs at public  schools were more likely to make tabloid newspaper headlines than similar stories at state schools. Mr  Sutton added that boarding schools also had to take precautions because, unlike day schools, they  stood in loco parentis and had legal responsibilities. Last year Eton, which is situated in Berkshire,  was one of many prominent public schools to expel pupils. Four Etonians were arrested outside a London  nightclub after they were seen handling ecstasy tablets, although no charges were brought.  <p>  <p>One parent of a former Etonian said yesterday that she was aware of drug use at the school,  predominantly cannabis and ecstasy.  <p>  <p>Ewa Lewis, social editor of the Tatler magazine, said: "Recreational drugs are now very fashionable  whether you go to Eton or Walthamstow High. It is prevalent in all schools. People seem to think that  the upper classes are some sort of dinosaur breed. They have exactly the same culture and fashions of  any other children.  <p>  <p>"Just because these children are at public school it doesn't mean they have pocketfuls of cash.  They haven't. Most are on very tight allowances. Most don't get the chance to work on a paper round or  on the weekend."   <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
