 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Bomber targets Barclays bank</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Bomber targets Barclays bank</b><br><br><br><b><h2>29 April 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Barclays on full  security alert  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Ian King</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Barclays Bank has intensified security arrangements for its annual meeting this Thursday in the  wake of extortion attempts by the so-called Mardi Gras bomber.  <p>  <p>Barclays, which has been sent 25 homemade bombs by the extortionist over the past 16 months, fears  that the bomber could attempt a 'spectacular' at the meeting. In the most recent attack, nine days  ago, a small device exploded outside a Barclays branch in Ealing, west London.  <p>  <p>A Barclays spokeswoman confirmed that security would be strengthened for Thursday's meeting at the  Queen Elizabeth II conference centre, in Westminster, but declined - for obvious reasons - to talk  about specific arrangements. She added: "Security will be tightened, and we are working with the people at the centre to ensure  this."  <p>  <p>Barclays is also being advised on the meeting by Scotland Yard, which has handled all negotiations  to date with the extortionist, and which initially corresponded secretly with him or her through the  personal columns of the Daily Telegraph.  <p>  <p>The fears about the Mardi Gras bomber mean Barclays has had problems with its annual meeting for  the third consecutive year. Two years ago, it withstood calls for the resignation of the then chairman, Andrew Buxton,  following complaints about boardroom pay and treatment of customer shareholders. A year ago, the AGM was picketed by members of UNIFI, the bank's staff union, who were protesting  about branch closures and redundancies.   <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" 