 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - 17th Century book of prayer available on CD-ROM</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Sevententh century book of prayer available on CDROM</b><br><br><br><b><h2>17 April  1996</h2></b><br><h2>Prayer book goes online in fight to attract new generation  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Madeleine Bunting</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>The traditionalist Prayer Book Society is taking its battle to win the minds of a new generation  online with a CDROM version of the 17th century 'Book of Common Prayer'.  <p>  <p>Priests planning the order of service will be able to tap in the type of service - wedding, funeral  or Eucharist - and date, and a computer program will do the rest, selecting the appropriate readings,  psalms, collects and hymns.  <p>  <p>The Prayer Book Society, anxious to shore up its diminishing appeal, has stolen a march on the  Church of England and the Catholic Church by being the first to commission the &#163;89 package of the  Prayer Book and King James I Bible, launched in London yesterday.  <p>  <p>"Priests will sit down at the computer to devise the Order which can then be printed on to a single  sheet," said David Drury of the Yorkshire software company which has produced the Book of Common  Prayer program. "It will be much easier because you won't have to dive around a service book trying to  find the right prayer or reading."  <p>  <p>The CDROM is to be launched in America, and sales are expected to reach more than 10,000.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT 