 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Diana's stalker struck off over drugs</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Diana's stalker struck off over drugs</b><br><br><br><b><h2>25 April 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Diana's  stalker struck off over drugs  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Gary Younge</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>A doctor arrested three times in two months for stalking the Princess of Wales was struck off the  medical register yesterday because of drugs offences.  <p>  <p>Klaus Wagner, aged 37, was committed to a mental hospital in March after his latest arrest for  stalking, but yesterday he appeared before the General Medical Council to answer the misconduct charge  after drug convictions last September.   <p>  Dr Wagner, an orthopaedic surgeon, was sentenced to 15 months in jail but was released immediately because of time spent on remand. The GMC took only 10 minutes to  decide to strike his name from the register after the committee was told that Dr Wagner's offences  included five of obtaining morphine-based drugs by deception, two of attempting to obtain drugs by  deception and one of possessing a Class A drug, codeine phosphate. The bogus prescriptions were  written out for collection from pharmacies in London, Kent, Essex, Lincolnshire and Cambridgeshire.   <p>  <p>Dr Wagner was sent to a psychiatric hospital in London last month after he had been seen carrying a  six-foot banner in the shape of a crucifix, with the words 'Elizardbeast, We are 666 of you'. He was  also seen distributing leaflets attacking the Queen. It is alleged he believes she is possessed by the  devil.   <p>  <p>Dr Wagner, of Stratford, east London, insisted that no evidence had been produced that any  patient had been at risk and no complaint had been made against him anywhere he had worked.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
