 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Louise Allen kicked to death after trying to break up funfair fight </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Louise Allen kicked to death after trying to break up funfair fight </b><br><br><br><b><h2>1 May 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Girls, 13, held on killing</h2><H3> Teenager kicked to death after trying to break up fight at funfair</H2>   <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Owen Bowcott</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Two 13-year-old girls were last night being questioned by Northamptonshire police after a teenager was kicked to death near a funfair after attempting to stop a fight.  <p>  <p>Louise Allen, of Corby, who was also 13, was put on a life support machine after the attack involving several teenagers in her home town on Monday evening. But it was switched off yesterday afternoon. Her parents had been at her bedside all day.  <p>  <p>The Rev Niall Sheridan, chairman of governors at Our Lady and Pope John School, where Louise had been a pupil, claimed her death was the result of a mindless act of violence.  <p>  <p>"She died trying to break up a fight," he said. "She was trying to make a little peace and got killed for her trouble. She was loved in the school, she was a member of a big extended family with lots of uncles, cousins and aunts. They are absolutely wrecked tonight. She was a sweet girl with a lovely personality."  <p>  <p>Louise had been walking back from the funfair when she came across a fight on Monday evening, Mr Sheridan said. She had been repeatedly kicked around the head during the incident.  <p>  <p>Louise's cousin, Nicola O'Neill, aged 14, yesterday laid flowers on the spot where the fight had taken place. Louise had gone to the aid of a friend, she said, who had been attacked by a girl from a rival school on grassland near the Stevens funfair. But Louise had then become the object of assault, dragged by her hair to the ground and then repeatedly kicked about the head.  <p>  <p>"She was a quiet girl, although when she was with her friends she had a good time," said Nicola. "I've only known her have one fight in her whole life before. That was last year when someone started picking on her and she just started back."  <p>  <p>The funfair owner, Charmaine Guest, said there had been no trouble at the fair and no one had known anything about the incident until some time after. Louise was fatally injured less than a mile from her home, in Steyning Close, on a large council estate in Corby. Friends reported that she had been asthmatic and there were suggestions that the assault had triggered an attack.  <p>  <p>A post mortem is being held at Kettering General Hospital, where Louise died. Northamptonshire police last night confirmed that two 13-year-old girls were being interviewed in custody. Detective Chief Inspector John Cordner said: "We are still trying to establish exactly what happened last night."  <p>  <p>Counselling sessions have been arranged for pupils at her school.   <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400