 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Radio 5 Live named UK station of the year in Sony radio  awards </TITLE></HEAD> <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea"  vlink="#adeaea"> <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right  BORDER="0"></A> <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br>
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Radio 5 Live named UK  station of the year in Sony radio awards </b><br><br><br><b><h2>18 May 1996</h2></b><br><h2>BBC  tops radio ratings  </h2>
 <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Andrew Culf</b><br><br>      <p> <p>The BBC has leapfrogged ahead of commercial radio in the ratings battle for the first  time in nearly two years, it was disclosed yesterday. A decline in listening to local  commercial stations combined with strong performances by Radio 1 and Radio 5 Live helped the  BBC regain pole position in the first three months of 1996. <p> <p>Viva!, the women's radio  station in London, which has been bought for &#163;3m by Mohammed Al Fayed's Liberty  Publishing, slumped to one of the lowest figures recorded with 11,000 listeners a week, fewer  than 0.1 per cent of its available audience. <p> <p>BBC radio gained a 50.4 per cent share of  the total radio audience between January and March, compared to 47.2 per cent in the final  quarter of 1995. Nearly 400,000 more listeners tuned into BBC services over the period, while  commercial radio's share slipped from 49.7 per cent to 47.6 per cent. The reversal contradicted  warnings by Liz Forgan, the former managing director of BBC network radio, who was credited  with successfully repositioning its five national stations before resigning earlier this year.  She said increasing competition would erode the BBC's share to 30 per cent within a decade. <p>  <p>Best performances were recorded by Radio 1, where breakfast show host, Chris Evans,  increased his weekly ratings from 6.2 million to 6.48 million adults, an increase of 280,000.  When under 15-year-olds are included the weekly audience is 7.36 million. <p> <p>Radio 5 Live,  named last month as national station of the year in the Sony radio awards, achieved a record  weekly audience of 5.21 million. BBC local and regional services also registered an increased  share. <p> <p>Sue Farr, head of marketing and publicity for network radio, said the figures  were robust and healthy. <p> <p>Douglas McArthur, managing director of the Radio Advertising  Bureau, denied the commercial sector faced a crisis, but said local stations would investigate  the decline. He said commercial radio had been the fastest growing advertising medium for three  years and had 30 per cent more listeners than three years ago. <p> <p>All the national  commercial stations, except Atlantic 252, registered increases. Talk Radio UK, which increased  its audience by six per cent to 2.1 million, has poached BBC radio's head of strategy and  development Paul Robinson as general manager. It intends to follow Radio 5 Live's success by  boosting its evening sports output. <p> <p> <p> <p> <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr> <td  width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td  width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td  width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td  width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG  SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td> <td width=40><A  HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr> <td align=left  valign=middle width=200><h2><A HR