 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Tories suffer heavy losses in local elections</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Tories suffer heavy losses in local elections</b><br><br><br><b><h2>3 May 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Tories took a thrashing</h2>  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>James Meikle</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>The Tories suffered wipe-out in at least 21 councils early today. They no longer have any councillors among the 99 on Manchester city council, and much of the rest of Tory Manchester was also Conservative-free. No representaives of John Major's party survive among 60 councillors in Salford, 60 in Oldham, 72 in Wigan, and 62 in Tameside. Newcastle-upon-Tyne is a Tory free-zone, joining neighbouring south Tyneside.  <p>  <p>On the south coast, Hastings, where troubles besetting the fishing industry caused a backlash against the Tories, went to the Liberal Democrats, with a 17-15 lead over Labour.  <p>  <p>The last four Tories disappeared in Labour Oxford, and the single remaining Tory lost in Norwich, while the last five went in Weymouth and Portland, where there is still no overall control.  <p>  <p>Knowsley on Merseyside, Halton in Cheshire, Nuneaton and Bedworth in Warwickshire, Tamworth and Cannock Chase, in Staffordshire, and Hereford all lost any tinge of blue, and the new unitary council of Stoke-on-Trent will start business next year without Conservative representation. Lincoln, Stevenage and Harlow lost all their Tories. Just one Tory councillor is left in Sheffield, Liverpool, Rotherham and Barnsley.   <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
