 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - New York cab drivers to get lessons in good manners</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>New York cab drivers to get lessons in good manners</b><br><br><br><b><h2>7 May 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Charm school? Waddayamean? Ask New York's cab drivers  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Ian Katz</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>It is one of the immutable verities of modern urban life: buses always come in threes, the weirdo always takes the seat next to yours, and cabbies in New York are always rude.  But now the city's authorities are attempting a feat no less ambitious than moving the Statue of Liberty to the Bronx. They aim to teach New York taxi drivers good manners.  <p>  <p>Henceforth, trainee cabbies - whose grasp of English rarely matches their command of obscenity - will be taught 50 courteous phrases such as: "I'm sorry if you think I am driving too fast, sir/ madam. I will slow down immediately."  <p>  <p>The Taxi and Limousine Commission's initiative is the latest in its long battle to smarten up the image of New York's yellow cabs.  <p>  <p>It has incorporated the use of phrases such as "Thank you for hailing me, sir/madam" into the two-hour exam which all cabbies must pass. Instead of the volley of expletives which typically follows the proffering of a large denomination bill, cabbies will be encouraged to say: "I am sorry but I am not required to change a $50 bill."  <p>  <p>News of the initiative had, by yesterday, evidently not reached some cabbies who responded to inquiries on the subject with the screech of spinning tyres.  Others replied with impeccable manners, but had difficulty deciphering the commission's recommended phrases.  <p>  <p>Mohamad Hassan, who has driven a cab since arriving from Egypt nine years ago, said: "Taxi driver treat the people very nice but people treat the taxi driver very bad."  He said that drivers were occasionally tetchy because they had been assigned "junk car".  <p>  <p>M D Hossain, a six-year veteran cabbie from Bangladesh, said: "I talk to passengers all the time, but I have a lot who get in the cab and treat me like an animal."  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
