 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - FA criticised for failing to drop Gazza from England squad over 5,000 damage to plane </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>FA criticised for failing to drop Gazza from England squad over 5,000 damage to plane </b><br><br><br><b><h2>31 May 1996</h2></b><br><h2>League gains Nationwide support  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Russell Thomas</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>The Football League yesterday put itself under &#163;5.25m Nationwide protection, only for the building society to find negative vibes already rattling the windows.  <p>  <p>Even such a solid financial institution as Nationwide, it seems, cannot escape the fall-out from the scandal of England's aeroplane vandalism. The fact that the prime suspect is such a high-profile player as Paul Gascoigne, whose 29th birthday celebrations allegedly resulted in &#163;5,000 damage, has inflated the adverse publicity.  <p>  <p>After the record three-year sponsorship deal was announced, Nationwide's chief executive Brian Davis admitted: "Our timing was a little bit unlucky with this story."  <p>  <p>Davis joined the widespread criticism of the FA's fumbling response to the aerial episode. "What's happened is very silly and should have been better managed," he said. "By the sound of it they had a bit of a wild party on the plane. It sounds very bad news. The FA will have to look into it and take the right action."  <p>  <p>But, overall, "this is the right time to join forces with the national game," Davis insisted. "We're aware that in business, as in sport, there will be incidents. But we have to look on the positive side." The Nationwide deal represents a 75 per cent increase on the League's previous &#163;1m-a-year three-year contract with Endsleigh Insurance.  <p>  <p>The League's bargaining power was strengthened by the recent five-year, &#163;125m television deal under which more than 60 live games a season will go out on Sky Sports from August. ITV will show highlights. Davis said the TV deal was "a real bonus" and added: "The national game has a very strong image. And the audiences all round are getting bigger." Gordon McKeag, the League president, conceded that the financial gap with the Premier League was "not bridgeable" but he believed that the TV and sponsorship deals would give the 72 member clubs a sounder financial base and help end talk of a breakaway to a Premiership second division. "We certainly hope that any dissension will be in the past," said McKeag, "And we hope these deals will cement things between all the member clubs. We've put together a package that gives our clubs the opportunity to stand on their feet."  <p>  <p>* England Under-21s lost any chance of reaching the Toulon tournament final after falling 3-1 to Portugal last night. Manchester United's Terry Cooke was sent off after 64 minutes for violent conduct and there were eight bookings, five for England. Dani, loaned to West Ham last season, scored Portugal's third goal after helping create the others. England replied through Tottenham's Steve Slade just after half-time.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td