 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Man named in hunt for M25 road rage killer</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Man named in hunt for M25 road rage killer</b><br><br><br><b><h2>1 June  1996</h2></b><br><h2>Tracing M25 'road rage' killer could take up to a year, but we'll get him, says  detective  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Duncan Campbell</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>It could take up to a year for the killer of a young man on the M25 two weeks ago to be traced, the  detective leading the murder hunt warned yesterday.  <p>  <p>Detective Superintendent Nick Biddis, of Kent police, said neighbours of owners of the type of car  driven by the murderer should contact the police if the vehicle has disappeared within the past 10  days. In another murder investigation, also involving a minor traffic incident, witnesses to the car  chase preceding it have come forward.  <p>  <p>Mr Biddis said in Canterbury that his team of 40 officers was now trying to trace all the owners of  the 7,500 L-registered Land Rover Discoveries in Britain. Initially, it had been reported that there  were 1,000. "We are not ringing them up, it is a case of actively visiting people. I want the offender  to know that because we could be banging on his door and I want him to worry about that.  <p>  <p>"It could take months or it could take the best part of a year to trace every single owner  currently on the police national computer." He remained confident that the man who fatally stabbed  Stephen Cameron, aged 21, on 19 May would be caught.  <p>  <p>Mr Biddis suggested that the murderer may have suffered injuries because blows were exchanged  before the knife was pulled. There was no evidence that Mr Cameron knew his attacker.  <p>  <p>In the other murder investigation, witnesses to a car chase in north London last Monday night have  come forward following appeals on Thursday, a police spokeswoman said.  <p>  <p>A Ghanaian man aged 35, on holiday from Germany, was shot dead after a driver pursued the car in  which he was travelling. There had earlier been a minor collision.  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
