 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Airlines to introduce handcuffs to restrain disruptive passengers  </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Airlines to introduce handcuffs to restrain disruptive passengers  </b><br><br><br><b><h2>6 June 1996</h2></b><br><h2>In-flight troublemakers face the threat of mile-high handcuffs  </h2>
  <br>By
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Nick Varley</b><br><br>      <p>  <p>Rowdy holidaymakers who take their in-flight enjoyment too far are to face a new deterrent: the mile-high cuffs. Airlines are introducing handcuffs to restrain passengers who become disruptive and potentially dangerous mid-flight.  <p>  <p>Crews have been assaulted and flights diverted to eject drunken travellers in previous incidents.  Now two of the biggest charter airlines, Air 2000 and Leisure International Airways, which will carry nearly four million passengers between them this summer, are hoping to prevent any repeats by threatening the use of the cuffs. A number of other airlines are considering whether to follow suit. A spokeswoman for Air 2000 said: "We are not talking about cuffs as seen on American cop shows - these would be plastic restraining devices." Leisure International Airways, formerly Air UK Leisure, which flies to the Mediterranean, Florida and the Caribbean, said it was introducing the cuffs after cabin crews had expressed concern about violence and verbal abuse from passengers.  <p>  <p>A spokeswoman said it was not the youngsters who generally caused problems. "Often it is the older ones. We do carry a lot of football supporters and we don't get trouble." A British Airways spokesman admitted it already carried restraints. "Staff are all trained to operate these devices but they are used very rarely and only then with the permission of the captain." But Richard Hedges, of Britannia Airways, the largest charter operator which carries eight million passengers a year, said it preferred other methods of dealing with in-flight problems. "We have no evidence there is a rise in incidents which require this sort of measure," he said.  <p>  <p>Perhaps if his airline carried England footballers, he would hold a different view.  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
