 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Guernsey votes to legalise abortion</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Guernsey votes to legalise abortion</b><br><br><br><b><h2>14 June 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Guernsey votes to make abortions legal  </h2>
  <br><br>      <p>The parliament of Guernsey yesterday voted to legalise abortion almost 30 years after it became legal in Britain. The move follows months of debate which has divided the island.  <p>  <p>After two days of debate, the States of Deliberation agreed to a proposal to repeal a law that makes having an abortion punishable by life imprisonment. The grounds for allowing abortion are similar to those on the mainland but slightly stricter.  <p>  <p>Unlike Britain, which places no time limit on abortions where there is a strong possibility of a serious risk of physical or mental abnormality in the child, Guernsey has placed a 24-week limit.  <p>  <p>It is also proposed that abortions should not be carried out after the 12th week of a pregnancy except where the health of the woman or child is at significant risk.  <p>  <p>In Britain abortions can be carried out up to 24 weeks, where it is thought the continuance of a pregnancy would cause greater harm to a woman or her family than if it was terminated.  <p>  <p>The parliament divided only on this clause. Voting was 22 for and 18 against. The proposals will now go to the island's law department which will draft a bill. This will then go to the Privy Council for final approval. Anti-abortionists, led by Cynthia Kennedy, a veteran of the American movement, have distributed graphic leaflets to thousands of homes. Pro-choice campaigners have responded with petitions.  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
