 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Teenager Jason Lidbury fined for taking 475 pigeons from  Trafalgar Square </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Teenager Jason Lidbury fined for taking 475 pigeons from Trafalgar Square </b><br><br><br><b><h2>2  July 1996</h2></b><br><h2>Youth fined for taking Trafalgar Square pigeons  </h2>
  <br><br>      <p>A teenager who whisked away boxfuls of pigeons from Trafalgar Square was yesterday fined &#163;475.  Jason Lidbury, 18, unemployed, put up to 40 of the birds in a box at a time, Bow Street magistrates  heard.  <p>  <p>Andrew Wiles, prosecuting, said a licensed pigeon food seller, Bernard Rayner, observed Lidbury  taking birds on a number of occasions. "He saw the man position a box and put food in front of it and  when the pigeons came, he took hold of them and put them in the box.  <p>  <p>"He estimated 40 or so birds would be in the box at one time. He remonstrated with the defendant  but the defendant indicated he would not stop doing it and at one stage Mr Rayner released some  birds." Police arrested Lidbury in the square on 5 March. "He said he was collecting the pigeons and  taking them to his uncle who had racing pigeons to see if any were suitable for breeding. He went on  to say he would try to sell some of them."  <p>  <p>Peter Caldwell, defending, said: "Mr Lidbury was seen on five occasions and on his account the  number of birds in the box never exceeded 25. He was giving those birds to his uncle and his uncle  would pay 20p a bird. His view was these animals were vermin and he did not think he was doing  anything wrong at the time."  <p>  <p>Lidbury, an unemployed painter and decorator, of Stockwell, south London, made about &#163;20 from  the deals. "He recognises, whatever he thinks of the birds, they do add character to London and what  he did was selfish. It was an act out of character."  <p>  <p>He pleaded guilty to six summonses brought by the RSPCA. He was fined &#163;100 for being in  Trafalgar Square on 5 March with intent to take wild birds and &#163;75 on each of five summonses,  including possessing wild birds for sale, and having wild birds in his control.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
