 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Terence Perkins wins court's permission to challenge armed forces for   discharging him for being gay</TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Terence Perkins to challenge armed forces for discharging him for being gay</b><br><br><br><b><h2>  19 July 1996</h2></b><br><h2> Court backs gay sacked by navy  </h2>
  <br><br>      <p>A former Royal Navy serviceman yesterday won permission to bring a legal challenge against a decision to discharge him from the armed forces because he is gay.  <p>  <p>Mr Justice Sedley ruled in the High Court that Terence Perkins, aged 27, of Bestwood, Nottingham, had "an arguable case" for judicial review that the Ministry of Defence blanket ban on homosexuals was contrary to the European Union's equal treatment directive.  <p>  <p>Peter Duffy, appearing for Mr Perkins, said the "inflexible policy" offended against the right of gays to "dignity and freedom" in employment. The case is likely to be referred to the European Court of Justice. The House of Lords recently upheld the ministry's right to enforce the ban. Outside court, Stephen Grosz, solicitor for Mr Perkins, said the case raised the issue of whether the directive applied to homosexuals.  <p>  <p>Mr Perkins, who joined the navy in 1991, revealed he was homosexual in August 1995. The navy's Special Investigations Branch told him homosexuality was 'inconsistent with service in the armed forces' and he was sacked. Earlier this year, the Lords refused to hear an appeal by four other sacked homosexual service personnel against a Court of Appeal ruling that the ban was not unlawful.  <p>  <p>Yesterday Mr Duffy told the High Court that his client was relying on a recent European Court of Justice ruling in the case of 'P' giving transsexuals protection from discrimination under the directive. 'P' was dismissed from an educational establishment by Cornwall county council after deciding to have a sex change operation. The European Court ruled this amounted to unlawful discrimination.  <p>  <p>Mr Duffy argued that the ruling extended to banning all discrimination on the grounds of sexual orientation.  Richard MacManus, for the Government, argued that homosexuals did not come within the scope of the ruling.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0 SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
