 <HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Guardian Year - Flight TWA 800 blown up </TITLE></HEAD>  <body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" alink="#adeaea" vlink="#adeaea">  <A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/stitle.gif" ALIGN=right BORDER="0"></A>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><blockquote><br><br> 
<!--INFOLINE--><b>Flight TWA 800 blown up </b><br><br><br><b><h2>19 July 1996</h2></b><br><h2>TWA criticised over delay in releasing victims' names </h2>
<h3>Sixteen high-school friends were  among those who died</h3>  <br><br>      <p>Details of the 230 passengers and crew who died in the TWA crash began to emerge last night, with  at least 16 of the victims coming from a Pennsylvania high school.  <p>  <p>Among the few victims named were a Briton, Christine Baily, aged 46, and an Irish emigrant, Vera  Feeney, from Kilmore, Co Roscommon, and her daughter Deirdre, aged 17.  <p>  <p>The wife of jazz saxophonist Wayne Shorter, Anna Maria Shorter, and the daughter of jazz singer Jon  Lucien, Dalila Lucien, were also on the flight. Neither a complete passenger list nor even a breakdown  of nationalities were issued by TWA yesterday, and the airline came under sharp criticism for its  handling of the disaster.  <p>  <p>Sixteen of the passengers belonged to the French club of Montoursville High School in north-eastern  Pennsylvania, on their way to Europe to improve their language skills. Forty French nationals are  known to have been on board.  <p>  <p>Late last night eight Italians victims of the crash were named, and another three people with  Italian names were expected to be named.  <p>  <p>The names of the flight's four cockpit crew and 14 flight attendants were also released. Captain  Steve Snyder of Connecticut, Captain Ralph Kevorkian of California, and flight engineer Richard  Campbell of Connecticut had all been with TWA for more than 30 years.  <p>  <p>New York's mayor, Rudolph Giuliani, criticised TWA's senior managers for leaving families in the  dark, saying it had fallen to him, working overnight Wednesday from an incomplete list, to confirm or  relieve people's fears. "It is the lack of upper management that is distressing," said Mr Giuliani,  who knew at least one person aboard TWA 800. "What happened is outrageous. All night upper-level  management was missing."  <p>  <p>A TWA spokesman, John McDonald, told the CBS news network by telephone from the company's  headquarters in St Louis the airline had begun notifying victims' families, but admitted to a delay.  <p>  <p>  <p>  <p>  <br><br><center><TABLE border=0><tr>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jan.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jandot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/feb.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/febdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/mar.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/mardot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/apr.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/aprdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/may.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/maydot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jun.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/jundot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/jul.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/juldot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/aug.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/augdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/sep.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/sepdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/oct.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/octdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/nov.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/novdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  <td width=40><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/dec.html"><IMG SRC="/g96/pix/decdot.gif" ALIGN=LEFT  BORDER="0"></A></td>  </tr></TABLE></center><center><TABLE height=30 width=400 border=0><tr>  <td align=left valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/byauthor/autha.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/b2auth.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=center valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/index.html"><IMG border=0  SRC="/g96/pix/g96.gif"></A></h2></td>  <td align=right valign=middle width=200><h2><A HREF="/g96/bymonth/Obitjan.html"><IMG border=0   SRC="/g96/pix/b2obit.gif"></A></h2></td>  </tr></table></center></BODY></HTML> 
